snippet.title: Bela And Martha Karolyi Break Their Silence About USA Gymnastics Scandals | Megyn Kelly TODAY
snippet.description:
Savannah Guthrie joins Megyn Kelly TODAY to talk about former USA Gymnastics team coordinators Bela and Martha Karolyi breaking their silence to her about the sexual abuse scandals rocking the sport. The Dateline exclusive “Silent No More” airs Sunday.
